Goal Representation: ['1. Find a cup.', '2. Fill the cup with water.', '3. Place the cup of water in the freezer.']

behavior find_cup(cup:item):
    body:
        achieve close_char(char, cup)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        if exists cup: item: is_cup(cup):
            bind cup: item where:
                is_cup(cup)
            find_cup(cup)
        else:
            foreach cup: item:
                if is_cup(cup) and not visited(cup):
                    observe(cup, "Locate the cup")
